fooditems.name: Baked Pasta
fooditems.description: Indulge in the cheesy goodness of baked pasta, a comforting classic

fooditems.name: Dosa
fooditems.description: Crispy South Indian dosa, a savory delight with a golden-brown texture

fooditems.name: Shahi Paneer
fooditems.description: Creamy and rich, Shahi Paneer is a regal Indian dish featuring tender paneer (cottage cheese) in a luxurious cashew-based sauce, fit for royalty.

fooditems.name: Shahi Pani Puri
fooditems.description: Delight in the explosion of flavors with Golgappe. These crispy, hollow spheres are filled with spicy tamarind water and a medley of tangy chutneys, making every bite a burst of taste.

fooditems.name: Dhokla
fooditems.description: Savor the light and fluffy goodness of Dhokla, a steamed Gujarati delicacy made from fermented rice and chickpea flour, often garnished with mustard seeds and fresh coriander, for a delightful and healthy snack.

fooditems.name: Samosa
fooditems.description: Enjoy the perfect snack, crispy triangular pastries filled with spiced potatoes, peas, and sometimes minced meat, offering a delightful blend of flavors and textures.

fooditems.name: Chicken Biryani
fooditems.description: Indulge in the aromatic delight of Biryani, a fragrant rice dish infused with spices and layered with tender meats or vegetables, creating a symphony of flavors that's a true culinary masterpiece.

fooditems.name: Hyderabadi Chicken Biryani
fooditems.description: Indulge in the aromatic delight of Hyderabadi Biryani, a fragrant rice dish infused with spices and layered with tender meats or vegetables, creating a symphony of flavors that's a true culinary masterpiece.

fooditems.name: Egg Cury
fooditems.description: Savor the comforting warmth of Egg Curry, a flavorful dish where boiled eggs are simmered in a rich and spicy tomato-based gravy, offering a satisfying combination of protein and spice.

fooditems.name: Dill, Potato, and Egg Salad
fooditems.description: No mayo here! Chopped hard-boiled eggs and cooked, diced potatoes are combined with cornichons, sliced shallots, and a lively Dijon dressing for a simple potluck side dish.

fooditems.name: Dill, Potato, and Egg Salad
fooditems.description: No mayo here! Chopped hard-boiled eggs and cooked, diced potatoes are combined with cornichons, sliced shallots, and a lively Dijon dressing for a simple potluck side dish.
